Job Description:
The New York City Housing Authority (NYCHA) is the nation’s largest public housing authority, with an operating budget of $3.4 billion and public housing and Section 8 programs that provide housing to over 600,000 New Yorkers. NYCHA is seeking a highly qualified and dynamic leader to serve as the Vice President (VP) for Operations Support Services.   

Reporting to the General Manager, and an integral member of NYCHA’s executive team, the VP serves as the Authority’s lead subject matter expert and advisor for all aspects of Heating, Elevators, and the Emergency Services Department.

